# Switch

A switch allows users to turn an individual option on or off.

<Resources pkg="@ibrains-design/switch" />

<Showcase id="Switch" />

**Features**

- Syncs with `disabled` state of fieldset
- Syncs with form `reset` events
- Can be toggled programmatically

